            <div type="edition">
               <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" n="1" xml:id="Prologue">
                  <label>Prologue</label>
                  <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit" xml:lang="gez" xml:id="Gadle">
                     <label>gadle</label>
                     <ab>
                       ዛቲ፡ መጽሐፍ፡ ገድለ፡ ጻማሆሙ፡ ለአቡነ፡ አሮን፡ መንክራዊ፡ ወዘከመ፡ ኀረያ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ለዳሬት፡ ደብር፡ ቅድስት፡
                     </ab>
                  </div>
               </div>
               <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" n="2" xml:id="MainPart">
                  <label>Main part</label>
                  <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit" xml:lang="gez">
                     <ab>
                        ስምዑ፡ <gap reason="omitted" extent="unknown"/> ዘኮነ፡ መካነ፡ ልደቱ፡ ለአሮን፡ <gap reason="omitted" extent="unknown"/> በሀገረ፡ 
                        ገብያ፡ ዘስማ፡ ሰጐዳ፡
                     </ab>
                  </div>
                  <div type="textpart" subtype="explicit" xml:lang="gez">
                     <ab>
                        በኑዛዜ፡ ቃልከ፡ ይትረሥዕ፡ ኵሉ፡ ኀዘንነ። ወተፈጸመ፡ መዋዕለ፡ ለሁ፡ ለአባ፡ አሮን፡ መንክራዊ፡ በረከቱ፡ 
                        <gap reason="omitted" extent="unknown"/> አሜን።
                     </ab>
                  </div>
               </div>
               <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" n="3" xml:id="Translatio">
                  <label>Translation of the body of the saint</label>
                     <listBibl type="clavis">
                        <bibl type="BHO" corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/D9KQXSXB"><seg type="book"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:BHO"/><title level="m">Bibliotheca hagiographica orientalis</title><title type="short">BHO</title><title level="s">Subsidia Hagiographica</title><author><t:name xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Socii Bollandiani</t:name></author><pubPlace>Bruxellis–Beyrouth</pubPlace><publisher>Apoud Editores–Imprimerie Catholique</publisher><date>1910</date><series><t:title xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" level="s">Subsidia Hagiographica</t:title><t:biblScope xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" unit="volume">10</t:biblScope></series><biblScope unit="volume">10</biblScope><note type="url">https://archive.org/stream/bibliothecahagi00peet</note><citedRange unit="item">2</citedRange></bibl>
                     </listBibl>
                  <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit" xml:lang="gez" xml:id="Taamer">
                     <label>Miracle</label>
                     <ab>
                       ስምዑኬ፡ ንዜንወክሙ፡ ካዕበ፡ ኦአኃው፡ ኑኃ፡ መከራት፡ <gap reason="omitted" extent="unknown"/>  ለቅዱሳን፡ በደብረ፡ ዳሬት፡ ከመ፡ 
                        መሥገርት፡ ዘወረደት፡ ውስተ፡ ዓለም፡
                     </ab>
                  </div>
                  <div type="textpart" subtype="explicit" xml:lang="gez">
                     <ab>
                         ወአብኡ፡ ንፍቀ፡ ሥጋሁ፡ ለመንክራዊ፡ አሮን፡ በክብር፡ ወበስብሐት፡ ወአንበርዋ፡ ለታቦቶሙ፡ ላዕለ፡ መቃብሪሁ፡ እስከ፡ ዮም፡ ወእስከ፡ 
                         ዛቲ፡ ዕለት፡<gap reason="omitted" extent="unknown"/> አሜን።
                     </ab>
                  </div>
                  <div type="textpart" subtype="Hymn" xml:lang="gez" xml:id="hymn">
                     <label>hymn</label>
                  </div>
               </div>
            </div>
         
